</a>



<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="2153">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$guo-shao-yu-34" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/guo-shao-yu-34" class="zg-link" title="郭绍宇">郭绍宇</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$meng-xiao-zhu-74" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/meng-xiao-zhu-74" class="zg-link" title="孟晓竹">孟晓竹</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2287253" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">（已完结，多图）<br>前情提要：<br><br>哎哟，我叫东尼大木，是一个中小企业社员，还不错哦。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/45833dee4a61c6bc647f5f063a784a75_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="360" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="480" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/45833dee4a61c6bc647f5f063a784a75_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="360" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="480" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/45833dee4a61c6bc647f5f063a784a75_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic2.zhimg.com/45833dee4a61c6bc647f5f063a784a75_b.jpg"><br>我厌倦了枯燥的都市生活，再也没有漂亮的让我疯狂的可爱女人。我想要去河南嵩山去学少林，把头发也剃成了吴克。<br>这是我的朋友捞逼，有问题我就会和他在这个酒馆接头，任何人都猜不到，这是我们的暗号。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/42402b43092a00bf0a706ee0acfc55a9_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="493" data-rawheight="479" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="493" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/42402b43092a00bf0a706ee0acfc55a9_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="493" data-rawheight="479" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="493" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/42402b43092a00bf0a706ee0acfc55a9_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic2.zhimg.com/42402b43092a00bf0a706ee0acfc55a9_b.jpg"><br>他是个武术家，什么刀枪电动棒他都耍的有模有样。<br>“放心大胆地去吧”捞逼说道，“把手慢慢交给我，放下心中的困惑。”<br><noscript><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/c04ec82aceeeb09fe9be712dc7e59736_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="541" data-rawheight="394" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="541" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/c04ec82aceeeb09fe9be712dc7e59736_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="541" data-rawheight="394" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="541" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/c04ec82aceeeb09fe9be712dc7e59736_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic3.zhimg.com/c04ec82aceeeb09fe9be712dc7e59736_b.jpg"><br>可惜出师未捷身先死，是你的侧脸倒在我的怀里，徒留我孤单在湖面成双。<br>我对着黑白照片开始想像，少林寺当年的模样。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/67af0bc498cad38f6a88cc2d6b0fe716_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="297" data-rawheight="328" class="content_image" width="297"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="297" data-rawheight="328" class="content_image lazy" width="297" data-actualsrc="http://pic3.zhimg.com/67af0bc498cad38f6a88cc2d6b0fe716_b.jpg"><br>——往事完<br><br>却说我跑遍了牧場又绕過了村庄，乔装打扮摸进少林寺，黑夜里偷袭，去攻击，烟雾当武器。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/cbe17c8a8665304bac2e20d956350320_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="477" data-rawheight="243" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="477" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/cbe17c8a8665304bac2e20d956350320_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="477" data-rawheight="243" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="477" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/cbe17c8a8665304bac2e20d956350320_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic1.zhimg.com/cbe17c8a8665304bac2e20d956350320_b.jpg"><br>少林寺有三十六房，每房都有一个师兄。要偷学武功就找大师兄，江湖难测，谁是强者 谁争一统武林的资格。<br><br>我不禁开始幻想起成为武林高手的那一天，我要回到学校找到当年那个瞧不起我的老师，告诉他眼睛你要擦亮，记住我的模样。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/1c53ff9a04a23bf3851741df8bd07c6a_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="399" data-rawheight="300" class="content_image" width="399"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="399" data-rawheight="300" class="content_image lazy" width="399" data-actualsrc="http://pic3.zhimg.com/1c53ff9a04a23bf3851741df8bd07c6a_b.jpg"><br>我說老师，我是不是真的不懂事。<br>听我念绕舌歌詞，欣赏我打拳的样子......<br><noscript><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/e90c031aa6440f9990f5edc6f6e4cae3_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="440" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/e90c031aa6440f9990f5edc6f6e4cae3_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="440" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="600" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/e90c031aa6440f9990f5edc6f6e4cae3_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic4.zhimg.com/e90c031aa6440f9990f5edc6f6e4cae3_b.jpg"><br>我想了想还是算了吧，考不上的好学校，可以不微笑就走。<br>静下心来，我偷偷摸进练功房，拉开帘子。嘿你别说，我专心偷窥的侧脸还蛮好看。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/d3edc1ce78cac45d72c80e1b3d86abf3_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="649" data-rawheight="484" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="649" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/d3edc1ce78cac45d72c80e1b3d86abf3_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="649" data-rawheight="484" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="649" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/d3edc1ce78cac45d72c80e1b3d86abf3_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic4.zhimg.com/d3edc1ce78cac45d72c80e1b3d86abf3_b.jpg"><br><noscript><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/86e23aa33b900d6901e6814e52cb6216_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="650" data-rawheight="485" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="650" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/86e23aa33b900d6901e6814e52cb6216_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="650" data-rawheight="485" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="650" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/86e23aa33b900d6901e6814e52cb6216_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic3.zhimg.com/86e23aa33b900d6901e6814e52cb6216_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/5bf080e9ba3350f3d8232a81877f66f6_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="650" data-rawheight="485" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="650" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/5bf080e9ba3350f3d8232a81877f66f6_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="650" data-rawheight="485" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="650" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/5bf080e9ba3350f3d8232a81877f66f6_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic3.zhimg.com/5bf080e9ba3350f3d8232a81877f66f6_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/f47100282bcbeb4f3bca5f4e2fe917e0_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="650" data-rawheight="485" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="650" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/f47100282bcbeb4f3bca5f4e2fe917e0_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="650" data-rawheight="485" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="650" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/f47100282bcbeb4f3bca5f4e2fe917e0_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic1.zhimg.com/f47100282bcbeb4f3bca5f4e2fe917e0_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/ef894796e7a2d5b41b2ce89b720ba6cd_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="427" data-rawheight="323" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="427" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/ef894796e7a2d5b41b2ce89b720ba6cd_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="427" data-rawheight="323" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="427" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/ef894796e7a2d5b41b2ce89b720ba6cd_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic2.zhimg.com/ef894796e7a2d5b41b2ce89b720ba6cd_b.jpg"><br>我好像看到了什么不得了的东西，但当时已经吓傻了，就是开不了口让你知道。<br><br>大师兄他……他右拳打开了天，化身为……奥特曼！<br><noscript><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/20ae09089bb67a67b7dbfd1c6264d236_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="526" data-rawheight="290" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="526" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/20ae09089bb67a67b7dbfd1c6264d236_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="526" data-rawheight="290" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="526" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/20ae09089bb67a67b7dbfd1c6264d236_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic3.zhimg.com/20ae09089bb67a67b7dbfd1c6264d236_b.jpg"><br>和他搭手的竟是，宇宙恐龙杰顿！<br>隔着距离欣赏正邪对立的两方<br>我握紧拳头开始习惯<br>那以牙还牙的手段<br>恐惧来自退让<br><noscript><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/02b3d132b5a33c919b587dc49d8bde87_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="472" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/02b3d132b5a33c919b587dc49d8bde87_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="472" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="640" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/02b3d132b5a33c919b587dc49d8bde87_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic4.zhimg.com/02b3d132b5a33c919b587dc49d8bde87_b.jpg"><br>两人话不投机是战在一处：<br><noscript><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/7ffdc7fe56b0886f63bfb812bc947b72_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="641" data-rawheight="427" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="641" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/7ffdc7fe56b0886f63bfb812bc947b72_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="641" data-rawheight="427" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="641" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/7ffdc7fe56b0886f63bfb812bc947b72_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic3.zhimg.com/7ffdc7fe56b0886f63bfb812bc947b72_b.jpg"><br>我一观那招式，正是哲学神功！<br><noscript><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/d07893976882a338cf2d150484dc4b9c_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="568" data-rawheight="436" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="568" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/d07893976882a338cf2d150484dc4b9c_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="568" data-rawheight="436" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="568" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/d07893976882a338cf2d150484dc4b9c_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic1.zhimg.com/d07893976882a338cf2d150484dc4b9c_b.jpg"><br>再看大师兄，已是真气逆行，经脉紊乱，只在旦夕之间，危矣危矣。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/78e16fae92f1161eb571e35c69582124_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="644" data-rawheight="474" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="644" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/78e16fae92f1161eb571e35c69582124_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="644" data-rawheight="474" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="644" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/78e16fae92f1161eb571e35c69582124_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic1.zhimg.com/78e16fae92f1161eb571e35c69582124_b.jpg"><br>正在偷学武功的我不禁替他捏一把汗。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/3b5f42907f66efce3748d15912223ef3_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="650" data-rawheight="482" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="650" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/3b5f42907f66efce3748d15912223ef3_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="650" data-rawheight="482" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="650" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/3b5f42907f66efce3748d15912223ef3_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic4.zhimg.com/3b5f42907f66efce3748d15912223ef3_b.jpg"><br>见局势不妙，大师兄终于使出了少林寺的最高禁术：Spectrum光线！<br><noscript><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/fe4fafd36327497457b5260ebbe2b66b_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="348" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="480" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/fe4fafd36327497457b5260ebbe2b66b_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="348" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="480" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/fe4fafd36327497457b5260ebbe2b66b_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic4.zhimg.com/fe4fafd36327497457b5260ebbe2b66b_b.jpg"><br>Spectrum光线的时域表示如下：<br><noscript><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/5268ad7d980986013e17336375a36b78_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="470" data-rawheight="375" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="470" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/5268ad7d980986013e17336375a36b78_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="470" data-rawheight="375" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="470" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/5268ad7d980986013e17336375a36b78_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic1.zhimg.com/5268ad7d980986013e17336375a36b78_b.jpg"><br>但是杰顿也是有备而来，他正面硬刚了Spectrum光线。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/8482b281825209e986f94c2b6e8df6a0_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="470" data-rawheight="349" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="470" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/8482b281825209e986f94c2b6e8df6a0_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="470" data-rawheight="349" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="470" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/8482b281825209e986f94c2b6e8df6a0_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic1.zhimg.com/8482b281825209e986f94c2b6e8df6a0_b.jpg"><br>并进行傅立叶变换，看穿了光线的基频。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/658dad37d7289bd86047b407a2ea8dc1_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="470" data-rawheight="376" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="470" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/658dad37d7289bd86047b407a2ea8dc1_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="470" data-rawheight="376" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="470" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/658dad37d7289bd86047b407a2ea8dc1_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic2.zhimg.com/658dad37d7289bd86047b407a2ea8dc1_b.jpg"><br><br>然后杰顿也放大了。<br>他放的大，就是一个放大电路：<br><noscript><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/f979f52fb7d2718fce821f2ea8241c64_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="300" data-rawheight="211" class="content_image" width="300"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="300" data-rawheight="211" class="content_image lazy" width="300" data-actualsrc="http://pic1.zhimg.com/f979f52fb7d2718fce821f2ea8241c64_b.jpg"><br>Spectrum光线以更强的能量反射了回去！<br><noscript><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/38999380041a216deee77233a461e922_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="470" data-rawheight="348" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="470" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/38999380041a216deee77233a461e922_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="470" data-rawheight="348" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="470" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/38999380041a216deee77233a461e922_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic3.zhimg.com/38999380041a216deee77233a461e922_b.jpg"><br>大师兄不慎中招<br><noscript><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/16ad3393d090b03cba2e971088a3d7f1_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="470" data-rawheight="346" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="470" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/16ad3393d090b03cba2e971088a3d7f1_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="470" data-rawheight="346" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="470" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/16ad3393d090b03cba2e971088a3d7f1_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic2.zhimg.com/16ad3393d090b03cba2e971088a3d7f1_b.jpg"><br>效果拔群。（大师兄自己克自己，其实他是龙系口袋妖怪）<br><noscript><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/fe1663803d460fd7268744f25413177f_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="470" data-rawheight="347" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="470" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/fe1663803d460fd7268744f25413177f_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="470" data-rawheight="347" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="470" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/fe1663803d460fd7268744f25413177f_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic4.zhimg.com/fe1663803d460fd7268744f25413177f_b.jpg"><br>我哭了。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/6e4e702ddfa8a7220194a7155d7ccba7_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="650" data-rawheight="481" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="650" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/6e4e702ddfa8a7220194a7155d7ccba7_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="650" data-rawheight="481" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="650" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/6e4e702ddfa8a7220194a7155d7ccba7_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic4.zhimg.com/6e4e702ddfa8a7220194a7155d7ccba7_b.jpg"><br>江湖太险恶，功夫也不是那么好练的。<br>尤其是傅立叶变换，被期待，被覆蓋，蜕变的公式我学不来。<br><br>回家之后，我蓄起了头发，干起了送报纸的平凡工作。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/4613584c2469e2d29aec3debb6195c1d_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="271" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="480" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/4613584c2469e2d29aec3debb6195c1d_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="271" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="480" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/4613584c2469e2d29aec3debb6195c1d_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic2.zhimg.com/4613584c2469e2d29aec3debb6195c1d_b.jpg"><br>直到那一天，我骑车在篱笆外的古道，却看见了不可思议的一幕。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/f83e4e67014f6ad469b769ffd1d260be_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="271" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="480" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/f83e4e67014f6ad469b769ffd1d260be_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="271" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="480" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/f83e4e67014f6ad469b769ffd1d260be_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic3.zhimg.com/f83e4e67014f6ad469b769ffd1d260be_b.jpg"><br>我知道命运的前列腺已经开始增生。<br><br>回忆里待续。<br><br>————————————————————————————————————<br><br>第二回（大结局）：《雅蔑蝶前传：大师兄的逆袭》<br><br>上回书说到，我骑单车送报纸，竟遇到骇人的一幕。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic3.zhimg.com/a55be1fe9d625c22ee5466e3e0de83f6_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="271" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="480" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/a55be1fe9d625c22ee5466e3e0de83f6_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="271" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="480" data-original="http://pic3.zhimg.com/a55be1fe9d625c22ee5466e3e0de83f6_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic3.zhimg.com/a55be1fe9d625c22ee5466e3e0de83f6_b.jpg"><br>此地正是<br><noscript><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/d5a811c682b1f9cb8457a1d79fe8faa9_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="389" data-rawheight="128" class="content_image" width="389">上次大战中，千年古刹毁于一旦。方丈神通广大，火速通过审批，从政府手中拿到了规划，新址都已经建好了。</noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="389" data-rawheight="128" class="content_image lazy" width="389" data-actualsrc="http://pic2.zhimg.com/d5a811c682b1f9cb8457a1d79fe8faa9_b.jpg">上次大战中，千年古刹毁于一旦。方丈神通广大，火速通过审批，从政府手中拿到了规划，新址都已经建好了。<br><br>再定睛一瞧：<br><br>粗……粗大事儿了！宇宙恐龙杰顿杀过来了！<br>近处的地球科学队员逃跑不迭，已经惨遭石化，面无人色。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/5e74c53837bf48e2bc04ca70138ded4b_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="704" data-rawheight="396" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="704" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/5e74c53837bf48e2bc04ca70138ded4b_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="704" data-rawheight="396" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="704" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/5e74c53837bf48e2bc04ca70138ded4b_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic4.zhimg.com/5e74c53837bf48e2bc04ca70138ded4b_b.jpg"><br>你说你出家人不好好礼佛，订什么报纸啊。<br>吾命休矣！我的眼角有翔滑过。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/d4e841358b1171aa6cb6aeba8777d047_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="450" data-rawheight="256" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="450" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/d4e841358b1171aa6cb6aeba8777d047_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="450" data-rawheight="256" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="450" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/d4e841358b1171aa6cb6aeba8777d047_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic4.zhimg.com/d4e841358b1171aa6cb6aeba8777d047_b.jpg"><br>（三个人的声音）屌下留人！！！大师兄来也！！！<br>我一看来人有三，正是：<br><br>孙悟空大师兄<br><noscript><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/6cbe91fd45227cb9ea3ac16d8d95b359_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="467" data-rawheight="352" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="467" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/6cbe91fd45227cb9ea3ac16d8d95b359_r.jpg">“咳咳咳，俺老孙一库！”</noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="467" data-rawheight="352" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="467" data-original="http://pic2.zhimg.com/6cbe91fd45227cb9ea3ac16d8d95b359_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic2.zhimg.com/6cbe91fd45227cb9ea3ac16d8d95b359_b.jpg">“咳咳咳，俺老孙一库！”<br><br><br>令狐冲大师兄，好像还带了位师太一起来的。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/1014c3db2c047727f07f7fbe19d977cb_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="481" data-rawheight="333" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="481" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/1014c3db2c047727f07f7fbe19d977cb_r.jpg">“抛开zen斗挽cei衣siu，be牵be挂系最基友。”</noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="481" data-rawheight="333" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="481" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/1014c3db2c047727f07f7fbe19d977cb_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic4.zhimg.com/1014c3db2c047727f07f7fbe19d977cb_b.jpg">“抛开zen斗挽cei衣siu，be牵be挂系最基友。”<br><br>最后是断水流大师兄<br><noscript><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/040ac59aaab7b40fbad3a0a3e4bfcdab_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/040ac59aaab7b40fbad3a0a3e4bfcdab_r.jpg">“你们啊，垃圾。”</noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="640" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/040ac59aaab7b40fbad3a0a3e4bfcdab_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic4.zhimg.com/040ac59aaab7b40fbad3a0a3e4bfcdab_b.jpg">“你们啊，垃圾。”<br><br><br>这下有救了！我情不自禁地敬了个标准的礼，低头看了看卫生巾，它更加鲜艳了。<br><noscript><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/02685638b1ac3b3e384119eef4764a60_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="440" data-rawheight="586" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="440" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/02685638b1ac3b3e384119eef4764a60_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="440" data-rawheight="586" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="440" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/02685638b1ac3b3e384119eef4764a60_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic1.zhimg.com/02685638b1ac3b3e384119eef4764a60_b.jpg"><br><br>且看三位大师兄各显神通：<br>孙悟空大师兄使出了“影之分身术”<br><noscript><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/0d760fd06e86e903a236c3811eec3d10_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="128" data-rawheight="127" class="content_image" width="128"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="128" data-rawheight="127" class="content_image lazy" width="128" data-actualsrc="http://pic1.zhimg.com/0d760fd06e86e903a236c3811eec3d10_b.jpg"><br><br>拔一根毫毛，吹出……<br><noscript><img src="http://pic2.zhimg.com/0517f5625b5c3fa0c087a71a691cf451_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="258" data-rawheight="333" class="content_image" width="258"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="258" data-rawheight="333" class="content_image lazy" width="258" data-actualsrc="http://pic2.zhimg.com/0517f5625b5c3fa0c087a71a691cf451_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/71999f0ea6dfae974b4a630f509953d7_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="289" data-rawheight="374" class="content_image" width="289"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="289" data-rawheight="374" class="content_image lazy" width="289" data-actualsrc="http://pic4.zhimg.com/71999f0ea6dfae974b4a630f509953d7_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/1352d901407e7e209a29ee2418c28380_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="460" data-rawheight="300" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="460" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/1352d901407e7e209a29ee2418c28380_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="460" data-rawheight="300" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="460" data-original="http://pic1.zhimg.com/1352d901407e7e209a29ee2418c28380_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="http://pic1.zhimg.com/1352d901407e7e209a29ee2418c28380_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="http://pic4.zhimg.com/d7bbce6771316e2deb789c48eeb3b7d3_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="478" data-rawheight="300" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="478" data-original="http://pic4.zhimg.com/d7bbce6771316e2deb789c48eeb3b7d3_r.jpg">吹出……大师兄你吹出来这些都有点不负责任啊。</noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="478" data-rawheight="300" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="478" data-original="http: